{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "engie-mca-api",
    "name": "ENGIE Allocation Processor API",
    "description": "Complete test collection for ENGIE Market Message Processing API\n\nPhipeline Architecture:\n- Column 1: Event Handler (Steps 1A-1F)\n- Column 2+4: Message Processor (Steps 2A-2E + 4A-4E)\n- Column 3: Message Validator (Steps 3A-3G)\n- Column 5: N-ACK Handler (Steps 5A-5D)\n- Column 6: Output Handler (Steps 6A-6B)\n\nTotal: 29 user stories processed end-to-end\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:5000",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Messages",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Process Valid AllocationSeries",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has required fields', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('messageId');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('status');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('responseType');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('errorCount');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('errorCodes');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Valid message returns ACK', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.equal('Delivered');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.responseType).to.equal('Ack');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.errorCount).to.equal(0);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('messageId_valid', pm.response.json().messageId);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"messageId\": \"msg-valid-001\",\n  \"xmlContent\": \"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"UTF-8\\\"?>\\n<AllocationSeries>\\n  <Header>\\n    <MessageId>msg-valid-001</MessageId>\\n    <Timestamp>2026-03-26T10:00:00Z</Timestamp>\\n    <Type>AllocationSeries</Type>\\n  </Header>\\n  <EAN>8714568009996</EAN>\\n  <ContractId>CONTRACT-12345</ContractId>\\n  <Quantity>100</Quantity>\\n  <Unit>kWh</Unit>\\n  <Period>2026-03-26</Period>\\n</AllocationSeries>\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/messages",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "messages"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Process a valid market message\n\nExpected Flow:\n- Step 1A-1F: Event Handler - Receive, validate XML\n- Step 2A-2E: Message Processor - Classify, prioritize\n- Step 3A-3G: Message Validator - All validations pass\n- Step 4A-4E: Response Handler - Generate ACK\n- Step 5A-5D: N-ACK Handler - Send ACK\n- Step 6A-6B: Output Handler - Deliver\n\nExpected Result: Delivered + Ack + No errors"
          }
        },
